extends ../layout

block title 
  title='KakuLearn | Choose Hiragana Quiz Level'
block content
    h1 Lvl 1 - Hiragana
    p Take this quiz to test your knowledge on the 46 basic hiragana characters.
    a.go_next(href='quiz') Quiz
    h1 Lvl 2 - Dakuten and Handakuten
    p Take this quiz to test your knowledge on the 25 diacritics of hiragana characters.
    a.go_next(href='dakuten_quiz') Quiz 
    h1 Lvl 3 - Combinations
    p Take this quiz to test your knowledge on hiragana combiantions such as きゃ (kya) or ぴゃ (pya).
    a.go_next(href='combinations_quiz') Quiz
    h1 Lvl 4 - Final Test 
    p The final test combines all the topics listed above. Are you up for the challange? Click the button below!
    a.go_next(href='final_test') Quiz
